A small feedback if i may.
I recently downloaded your "Young Adult" and "What's your Number".  I noticed some patchiness (squares) in the samples.
I know it was long ago and you have UP-ed the bitrate since. But if you are using the same settings maybe you could give it a second thought, because i found another torrent (YIFY, 26K respectively) for each of the above, same size but beter (perceived) quality. Just an FYI.

PS: And, am not the one who gives you negative ratings :)
